1.01

    - more flexible interface for Plugin::CSRFDefender

1.00

    - bump up version

0.44

    - added Amon::Plugin::FillInFormLite.

0.43

    * e657339 [BUG] Amon::Util must not returns undef at 2nd time function call.
    * 7cfef62 Plugin::FillInForm: adjust content-length after fill-in.
    * updated docs

0.42

    - added Text::Xslate support
    - fixed some issues

0.41

    - added $req->uri_with() method.
    - added new option 'open_layer' to Amon::V::MT.

0.40

    - Amon::Web::Dispatcher::HTTPxDispatcher was removed.
    - Amon::Web::C was removed.
      use Amon::Web::Declare instead.

0.32

    - M::P::Object is no longer needed
    - ConfigLoader is enabled by default.
    - depend to latest Plack
    - Plugin::HTTPSesssion: pass $c to callback

0.31

    - Amon::Web::Dispatcher::HTTPxDispatcher will remove on 0.40
    - do not depend to Module::Pluggable::Object.
      New loader will die if one of controller has a syntax error.

0.30

    [SOME INCOMPAT CHANGES]
    - added Amon::ConfigLoader
    - make container as more simple
    - use class-data-inheritable in container
    - $c->view method move to Amon::Web
    - added Amon::Web->render()
    - added Amon::Web->render_partial()

0.22

    - Factory class was deprecated.
    - DBIx::Skinny is no longer default ORM.
      (Amon should not select any ORM as default)
    - move uri_for to Amon::Web

0.21

    - fixed tests
    - Amon::Sense::add_trigger should take multiple triggers.
    - [bug fixed] hook with instance should work
    - fixed deps
    - move redirect method to Amon::Web.

0.20

    - added Web::Dispatcher::Lite
    - Web::Dispatcher::RouterSimple:
        enable stricture automatically

0.19

